reviewText: Super hot, utterly French examination of the sexual life of a French Family.  I thought it was very moving and frank.
Movie is good but if you want the unedited version keep looking. It does not say it is edited on the description.  I'm going to keep looking for the uncut version.
i have first seen this movie in Netflix and i loved it. It depicts the stresses of teens on urges of sexuality.
Unrated version is watered down, and it isn't advertised as not being the original.
A very interesting storyline and a gorgeous cast. The physical scenes were edited but still enjoyable  to watch.
